    • Constructor Detail

      • Player

        public Player(java.lang.String name,
      int money,
      java.lang.String color)
        The default constructor of the player class. sets the location of player to integer array containing 2 and 0 by default. sets the inJail of player to false by default. sets the hasCompedRoom of the player to false by default sets the renovationSuccess of the player to false by default sets the specialOnlinePricing of the player to false by default sets the ReserveRent of the player to false by default sets the buildings of the player to HashMap with LandCard object as key and integer array as a value by default sets the cardsWithColor of the player to HashMap with String as a key and integer array as a value which are coming from reading color.txt sets the jailRound of the player to 0 by default
        Parameters:
        color - The color of the player's item on the board
        name - The name of the player
        money - The money of the player that he initially has
